Users are not allowed to terminate/Close the Command Prompt running the backup on log on and are required to wait for backup script to finish. The Command prompt will automatically close when done.

Users are recommended to backup files every week using the software provided to back up files.

Users are required to back up files every 2 weeks using the software provided to back up files.

Only qualified persononnels are allowed to restore files.

When qualified personnel couldn't restore file using the given software. The qualified personnel shall contact the service provider.
